WEBVTT

00:01:30.379 --> 00:01:32.103
Ilieleweka hakika,

00:01:32.127 --> 00:01:34.934
hawakuwa na furaha juu ya maswali yetu,

00:01:34.958 --> 00:01:38.707
na tuseme tu tulipata mgao mzuri 
wa "ukweli mbadala".

00:01:38.731 --> 00:01:41.412
(Kicheko)

00:01:41.436 --> 00:01:44.634
Wanaijeria wenye ushawishi mkubwa 
walikuwa wakituambia wakati ule

00:01:44.658 --> 00:01:46.655
kuwa tulikuwa washamba.

00:01:46.679 --> 00:01:49.883
hatukuelewa hali ya siasa ya Naijeria.

00:01:50.900 --> 00:01:52.995
Lakini pia walituambia

00:01:53.019 --> 00:01:55.627
kuwa habari ya wasichana wa Chibok

00:01:55.651 --> 00:01:56.836
illikuwa mzaha.

00:01:58.265 --> 00:02:00.965
Cha kusikitisha ni kuwa 
habari hii ya mzaha imedumu